<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Claude Prompting Cheat Sheet — Tax Workflow</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0d0f14;
    --surface: #14171f;
    --card: #1a1e28;
    --border: #252a38;
    --accent: #4fffb0;
    --accent2: #4fa8ff;
    --accent3: #ffb84f;
    --accent4: #ff6b6b;
    --text: #e8eaf0;
    --muted: #6b7280;
    --tag-bg: #1f2435;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 40px 20px;
  }

  .page {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Header */
  .header {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    padding-left: 20px;
  }
  .header-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .header h1 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .header h1 span { color: var(--accent); }
  .header p {
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* Section label */
  .section-label {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  /* Cards grid */
  .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; }
  .grid-1 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 14px; }

  @media (max-width: 600px) { .grid-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 20px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }

  .card-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .card-icon {
    width: 32px; height: 32px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 16px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .green  { background: rgba(79,255,176,0.12); }
  .blue   { background: rgba(79,168,255,0.12); }
  .yellow { background: rgba(255,184,79,0.12); }
  .red    { background: rgba(255,107,107,0.12); }

  .card-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .card-subtitle {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 1px;
  }

  /* Prompt rows */
  .prompt-row {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .prompt-row:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0; border-bottom: none; }

  .prompt-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .prompt-text {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--accent);
    background: rgba(79,255,176,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(79,255,176,0.15);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .prompt-text.blue-p {
    color: var(--accent2);
    background: rgba(79,168,255,0.05);
    border-color: rgba(79,168,255,0.15);
  }
  .prompt-text.yellow-p {
    color: var(--accent3);
    background: rgba(255,184,79,0.05);
    border-color: rgba(255,184,79,0.15);
  }
  .prompt-text.red-p {
    color: var(--accent4);
    background: rgba(255,107,107,0.05);
    border-color: rgba(255,107,107,0.15);
  }

  /* Big tip card */
  .tip-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(79,255,176,0.08), rgba(79,168,255,0.06));
    border: 1px solid rgba(79,255,176,0.25);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin-top: 14px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .tip-icon { font-size: 22px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
  .tip-body {}
  .tip-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .tip-text {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .tip-text strong { color: var(--text); }

  /* Formula table */
  .formula-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .formula-table th {
    text-align: left;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .formula-table td {
    padding: 10px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    vertical-align: top;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .formula-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .formula-table td:first-child {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--accent3);
    white-space: nowrap;
    width: 140px;
  }
  .formula-table td:last-child { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; }

  /* Tags */
  .tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; margin-top: 10px; }
  .tag {
    background: var(--tag-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 3px 9px;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  /* Footer */
  .footer {
    margin-top: 48px;
    padding-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .footer span { color: var(--accent); }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="header">
    <div class="header-eyebrow">Carlos Olivencia Tax Services</div>
    <h1>Claude Prompting<br><span>Cheat Sheet</span></h1>
    <p>Tax workflow edition — ProConnect · QBO · Clients · Documents</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Section 1: Context Setting -->
  <div class="section-label">01 — Set the Stage First</div>
  <div class="grid-2">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="card-icon green">🎯</div>
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Role Setting</div>
          <div class="card-subtitle">Tell Claude who it is</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="prompt-row">
        <div class="prompt-label">Tax Advisor Mode</div>
        <div class="prompt-text">"Act as a tax professional helping me prepare a Schedule C return for a self-employed client."</div>
      </div>
      <div class="prompt-row">
        <div class="prompt-label">Software Guide Mode</div>
        <div class="prompt-text">"You are a ProConnect Tax expert. Walk me through [task] step by step."</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="card-icon blue">🔧</div>
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Software Context</div>
          <div class="card-subtitle">Specify your stack</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="prompt-row">
        <div class="prompt-label">Stack Declaration</div>
        <div class="prompt-text blue-p">"I use ProConnect Tax and QuickBooks Online Accountant. Don't give me Drake or Lacerte instructions."</div>
      </div>
      <div class="prompt-row">
        <div class="prompt-label">Workflow Context</div>
        <div class="prompt-text blue-p">"I'm in QBOA → Prep for Taxes. Where do I go next to import into ProConnect?"</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Section 2: Deductions & Strategy -->
  <div class="section-label">02 — Deductions & Tax Strategy</div>
  <div class="grid-2">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="card-icon yellow">💰</div>
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Deduction Stacking</div>
          <div class="card-subtitle">Reduce balance owed</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="prompt-row">
        <div class="prompt-label">Start with facts</div>
        <div class="prompt-text yellow-p">"My client has $[X] net self-employment income. Before recommending deductions, ask me what you need to know about their situation."</div>
      </div>
      <div class="prompt-row">
        <div class="prompt-label">Targeted ask</div>
        <div class="prompt-text yellow-p">"What retirement contribution options can reduce SE tax for a sole proprietor with $80K net profit?"</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="card-icon green">📋</div>
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Specific Forms</div>
          <div class="card-subtitle">Form-level questions</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="prompt-row">
        <div class="prompt-label">Schedule C</div>
        <div class="prompt-text">"Where on Schedule C does home office go? What form do I attach?"</div>
      </div>
      <div class="prompt-row">
        <div class="prompt-label">QBI / 199A</div>
        <div class="prompt-text">"Does QBI apply if my client's taxable income is already negative? Should I still enter it in ProConnect?"</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Section 3: Step-by-Step Control -->
  <div class="section-label">03 — Control the Pace</div>
  <div class="card grid-1">
    <div class="card-header">
      <div class="card-icon blue">🐢</div>
      <div>
        <div class="card-title">Step-by-Step Prompts</div>
        <div class="card-subtitle">One action at a time — your preferred style</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="prompt-row">
      <div class="prompt-label">Slow walk</div>
      <div class="prompt-text blue-p">"Walk me through this one step at a time. Wait for me to confirm before giving the next step."</div>
    </div>
    <div class="prompt-row">
      <div class="prompt-label">Pause & confirm</div>
      <div class="prompt-text blue-p">"Give me only Step 1. I'll tell you when I'm ready for Step 2."</div>
    </div>
    <div class="prompt-row">
      <div class="prompt-label">Resume where you left off</div>
      <div class="prompt-text blue-p">"We were on Step 2 of the Prep for Taxes workflow. I completed it. Continue from Step 3."</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Section 4: Client Docs & Letters -->
  <div class="section-label">04 — Client Documents & Letters</div>
  <div class="grid-2">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="card-icon yellow">✉️</div>
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Formal Letters</div>
          <div class="card-subtitle">PDF-ready output</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="prompt-row">
        <div class="prompt-label">Letter request</div>
        <div class="prompt-text yellow-p">"Write a formal letter to my client explaining why they owe taxes this year. Tone: professional but reassuring. Generate it as a downloadable PDF."</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="card-icon red">⚠️</div>
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Notice Response</div>
          <div class="card-subtitle">IRS / state notices</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="prompt-row">
        <div class="prompt-label">Analyze a notice</div>
        <div class="prompt-text red-p">"I received a notice from [IRS / NYS / PR Hacienda]. Here's what it says: [paste text]. What does it mean and what action is required?"</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Section 5: Clarification Control -->
  <div class="section-label">05 — Make Claude Ask Before Assuming</div>
  <div class="tip-card">
    <div class="tip-icon">💡</div>
    <div class="tip-body">
      <div class="tip-title">The Golden Rule for Your Workflow</div>
      <div class="tip-text">
        Add this line to any prompt where client details matter:<br><br>
        <strong>"Before making any recommendations, ask me the questions you need about this client's situation."</strong><br><br>
        This prevents Claude from assuming a client has a car, home office, or other deductions before you've confirmed the facts.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Section 6: Formula -->
  <div class="section-label">06 — The Power Prompt Formula</div>
  <div class="card">
    <table class="formula-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Component</th>
          <th>What to include</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>[ROLE]</td>
          <td>Who Claude should be — "tax professional," "ProConnect expert," "QBO guide"</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>[CONTEXT]</td>
          <td>Software, client situation, jurisdiction, year — the facts that matter</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>[TASK]</td>
          <td>Exactly what you want — walkthrough, letter, table, analysis, form entry</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>[CONSTRAINT]</td>
          <td>Format, pace, assumptions — "step by step," "don't assume," "PDF output"</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>[CLARIFY]</td>
          <td>Optional — "Ask me what you need before starting"</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <div class="tags">
      <span class="tag">ProConnect</span>
      <span class="tag">QBOA</span>
      <span class="tag">Schedule C</span>
      <span class="tag">SEP-IRA</span>
      <span class="tag">Solo 401k</span>
      <span class="tag">QBI / 199A</span>
      <span class="tag">1040-X</span>
      <span class="tag">Books-to-Tax</span>
      <span class="tag">PR Hacienda</span>
      <span class="tag">NYS</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <div class="footer">
    <div>Carlos Olivencia Tax Services · <span>Claude.ai</span> Prompting Guide</div>
    <div>Tax Year <span>2024–2025</span></div>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
